All airport operators in this State shall maintain a roster of aircraft based or hangared at the facility. This roster shall include for each aircraft:
The "N" number, type, and model of the aircraft;
The name and address of the owner or operator of the aircraft, and the period of time the aircraft has been based or hangared at the facility;
The liability insurance policy or binder number;
The name of the insurance company shown on the policy; and
The name of the insurance producer.
